{"name":"Defense-Botch","img":"systems/dsa5/icons/dice/d20mu.svg","description":"Instead of suffering a standard 1D6+2 DP for a defense botch, you can roll on the following table. If the combatant is unarmed and rolls a 6 or less, add 5 to the result.","results":[{"_id":"cWg4hhULa2t8clAr","type":0,"text":"The weapon is irreparably destroyed. If the weapon is unbreakable, it falls to the ground.","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"systems/dsa5/icons/dice/d20mu.svg","rangeL":2,"rangeH":2},{"_id":"tIKaoYDSkqMBjvpm","type":0,"text":"You cannot use the weapon until it is repaired. If the weapon is unbreakable, it falls to the ground.","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"systems/dsa5/icons/dice/d20mu.svg","rangeL":3,"rangeH":3},{"_id":"txSHKVkr1xbLR7XU","type":0,"text":"The weapon is damaged. All checks against Attack or Parry suffer a penalty of 2 until the weapon is repaired. If the weapon is unbreakable, it falls to the ground.","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"systems/dsa5/icons/dice/d20mu.svg","rangeL":4,"rangeH":4},{"_id":"9OMCCXCFiEgq0alB","type":0,"text":"The weapon falls to the ground.","weight":1,"range":[5,5],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"systems/dsa5/icons/dice/d20mu.svg","rangeL":5,"rangeH":5},{"_id":"A0TRFdWwU2MYytem","type":0,"text":"The hero’s weapon is stuck in a tree, a wooden wall, the ground, or something similar. Freeing it takes 1 action and a check using Feat of Strength (Dragging & Pulling) with a penalty of 1.","weight":1,"range":[6,6],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"systems/dsa5/icons/dice/d20mu.svg","rangeL":6,"rangeH":6},{"_id":"yrboAegh9Ju1dGC7","type":0,"text":"Make a check using Body Control (Balance) with a penalty of 2, or fall to the ground and receive the state prone.","weight":1,"range":[7,7],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"systems/dsa5/icons/dice/d20mu.svg","rangeL":7,"rangeH":7},{"_id":"bPjOYHCVL3eKHvCt","type":0,"text":"Stumble and suffer a penalty of 2 on your next action.","weight":1,"range":[8,8],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"systems/dsa5/icons/dice/d20mu.svg","rangeL":8,"rangeH":8},{"_id":"Fo25J2SPOodMWl5C","type":0,"text":"Suffer one level of the condition Pain for 3 combat rounds.","weight":1,"range":[9,9],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"systems/dsa5/icons/dice/d20mu.svg","rangeL":9,"rangeH":9},{"_id":"mFhcXmAA9Pcq4XAg","type":0,"text":"Bump your head in the chaos of combat and suffer one level of Stupor for one hour.","weight":1,"range":[10,10],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"systems/dsa5/icons/dice/d20mu.svg","rangeL":10,"rangeH":10},{"_id":"J8wdZ3JSDCEoKsCW","type":0,"text":"Hurt yourself. Suffer your weapon’s damage, including the damage bonus (ignoring PRO). Unarmed combatants suffer 1D6 DP (ignoring PRO).","weight":1,"range":[11,11],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"systems/dsa5/icons/dice/d20mu.svg","rangeL":11,"rangeH":11},{"_id":"0TejvR31LVkvzmzp","type":0,"text":"Suffer double your weapon’s damage, including the damage bonus (ignoring PRO). Unarmed combatants suffer 2D6 DP (ignoring PRO).","weight":1,"range":[12,12],"drawn":false,"flags":{},"img":"systems/dsa5/icons/dice/d20mu.svg","rangeL":12,"rangeH":12}],"formula":"2d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"DuPORyMy1IVtkIcO":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"RollTable.s3YHPkVNXwfPzxy7"}},"_id":"3N2ZYFVDVn2TFqu8"}
